export const getTeasers = (name) => [
    `The palm does not lie, ${name}. What is encoded in your lines is both beautiful and sobering — a soul standing at the edge of its most important chapter yet. There is something the universe has been building toward in your life for longer than you have been conscious of. I have shown you only the surface. The depths are far more revealing. This card is meant to be shared with those who need to understand what makes you singular.`,
    `${name}, I have read many palms. What I see in yours is unusual — not in a comfortable way. The lines carry the specific signature of a life about to change in ways you have not yet permitted yourself to fully imagine. What I can share freely is only a fraction of what the full reading holds. Trust that this glimpse contains exactly what needs to reach the person receiving it.`,
    `The marks on your hand tell a story that begins long before this life and extends far beyond what is visible from where you are standing. ${name}, the convergence I see in your lines happens rarely — and when it does, it always precedes something significant. I have only begun to read it. These words are a seed meant to germinate in the minds of those who see them.`,
    `${name}, there are people who come to me and the lines say very little. Then there are people like you — where every mark is vivid, layered, insistent. Your palm is asking to be read fully. What I have shown you here is the opening of something considerably longer. Let this shared card be an introduction to the depth that exists within you.`,
    `What I see in your palm, ${name}, I was not entirely expecting. The combination of lines you carry does not appear often. I have given you the outline. The full picture is far more specific, and considerably more urgent. The person who receives this will sense that urgency and will be changed by the knowing of it.`,
    `${name}, the lines of your palm carry an energy I can only describe as unresolved — in the way that an unfinished sentence carries more weight than a completed one. Something in your life is reaching for a conclusion it has not yet found. The full reading makes clear what that is. This fragment is an invitation to move toward resolution.`,
    `I need you to understand something, ${name}: what I have shared so far is the version of your reading that requires no courage to receive. The rest — encoded more deeply in your lines — is the part that will matter. The part that, once heard, you will not be able to unfeel. What you share from here is your truth, spoken aloud.`,
    `Your palm speaks in a voice I do not often encounter, ${name}. There are layers here that a single glance cannot surface — a past that explains a present you have been struggling to understand, and a future closer and more specific than what I have described. Those who love you will understand more of themselves through understanding more of you.`,
    `${name}, the surface of your palm tells one story. Below the surface, in the depth and quality of the lines themselves, there is another story entirely. The one beneath is older, stranger, and considerably more illuminating. What I have shown you is the prologue. What comes next is yours to write and share.`,
    `There is something particular about your palm, ${name} — a marking I noticed immediately and have been deciding how to name. It speaks of a crossroads approaching on a specific timeline. The full reading tells you what I see there. This card holds the weight of that crossing, and the choice that waits for you.`,
    `${name}, I have been reading palms long enough to know when a hand is asking for something more than a surface reading. Yours is. The lines are precise, specific, and — in places — urgent. What cannot be said briefly is what matters most. Share this knowing with those brave enough to receive it.`,
    `The line of your fate, ${name}, carries within it the evidence of a life that has already pivoted more than once and is preparing to pivot again. I can see the shape of what is coming. The full reading names it directly. Let those who care about you glimpse the pivot that approaches.`,
  ];

